title: Vertiv Avocent ACS 8000: Active sessions
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/network/vertiv
license: GPL
distribution: kuhn-ruess
description:
 Reports the number of active user sessions on a Vertiv Avocent ACS 8000
 console server, taken from acsActiveSessionsNumberOfSession
 ({.1.3.6.1.4.1.10418.26.2.2.1.0}).

 Upper levels for the session count can be configured via the WATO
 ruleset {Vertiv ACS active sessions}. By default no levels are applied.

 Performance data:
  - {sessions} (current count of active sessions)

inventory:
 A single service per host is created.
